Run the scripts in this general order:

- ./install_mysql_ebs.sh
- ./install_application_dependencies.sh
- this will also involve adding your key to github. http://help.github.com/mac-set-up-git/ On this machine, run:
  ssh-keygen -t rsa
  Then copy/paste the key into github. Deployer keys won't work, because we deploy several projects from 1 key.
- scp a database dump to this server, ecom_datadump.sql
  init_db.sh -D lla_ecom_production -U lla_ecom_prod -L ecom_datadump.sql
- scp a database dump to this server, forum_datadump.sql
  init_db.sh -D lla_forum_production -U lla_forum_prod -L forum_datadump.sql
- run the application's capistrano deployment script to push the apache app configs out. Then a2ensite SITE, then restart apache.

You are done!
